Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.64,0:00:47.27,Danna ga Nani Main,kaoru,0,0,0,,Talvez eu possa cozinhas um pouco de carne e batatas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:52.53,Danna ga Nani Main,hajime,0,0,0,,Seriam estas... pequenas batatas em pó?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:00:53.11,Danna ga Nani Main,kaoru,0,0,0,,Sim...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:54.86,Danna ga Nani Main,hajime,0,0,0,,Munch, munch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:56.06,Danna ga Nani Main,hajime,0,0,0,,Está bom.
