Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:44.51,Danna ga Nani Main,kaoru,0,0,0,,C-Como está?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:51.19,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:52.27,Danna ga Nani Main,kaoru,0,0,0,,Eba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:56.54,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Ah, mas se você ficar boa na cozinha, nossa balança irá...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:02:58.03,Danna ga Nani Main,kaoru,0,0,0,,É-É mesmo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:59.57,Danna ga Nani Main,kaoru,0,0,0,,Aliás, por que você tirou a camisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:00.28,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Tirei?
